name: RandomWorkout
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: random workout
des: Great way to wake up in the morning, get fit during commercial breaks, and get your heartrate up after sitting around too long. New workouts added frequently. Just say Alexa Random Workout to get started. Please leave any comments for features you would like to see added to this skill, or any workout requests. Don't forget to ask Alexa to play some music before your workout!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
